1
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:07,800
Oh.

2
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,479
Where are you two kids

3
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:12,120
going?

4
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:18,960
Why are you here?

5
00:02:21,920 --> 00:02:23,440
To save you, your master

6
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:26,400
is fighting the ten demon soldiers led by Jin Wang.

7
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:30,000
But there are only three of them.

8
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:33,700
I think they are just throwing an egg against a rock.

9
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:35,440
Lady Tu sent me to guard you

10
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:36,320
just in case.

11
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:37,400
As expected,

12
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:38,880
you almost escaped.

13
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:42,220
And you even want to take her medicine ingredient away.

14
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:44,760
Master really came to save me.

15
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,000
Wait a minute.

16
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,040
Three people.

17
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,930
Also Sister Gesang and Lord Hu San.

18
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,280
My master is a deity.

19
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:54,800
Whatever Tu Goddess,

20
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,360
in front of my master, she's just like you,

21
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,560
a wild village demon.

22
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:00,400
Reckless thing.

23
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:03,000
Since your master is here anyway,

24
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:05,040
I'll kill you right now

25
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:07,400
so your foul mouth can never speak again.

26
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:09,880
Ancestor,

27
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:12,240
leave this guy to me.

28
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:13,840
You go deal with Tu Luohua.

29
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:15,720
If we don't get rid of her,

30
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:18,000
none of us will have a good life.

31
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:19,880
Spirits of heaven and earth,

32
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:20,720
spanning the vast universe,

33
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:21,800
reaching everywhere.

34
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:22,240
Flash!

35
00:03:26,440 --> 00:03:27,400
Do you think

36
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:30,160
you can stop me?

37
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:31,720
I can't stop you,

38
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:34,060
but the immortal spirit within me

39
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,400
might be able to.

40
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,320
Immortal spirit?

41
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,920
I didn't want to use this move.

42
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:43,180
I'm afraid of being possessed by the master within.

43
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,120
But now,

44
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,720
it's the only way.

45
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,320
Watch closely.

46
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,079
This move

47
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:52,370
is going to be very cool.

48
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:27,480
Let's see

49
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:30,460
how long you can keep up this appearance.

50
00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:34,720
Immortal.

51
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:37,650
Immortals are exactly what I slay.

52
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:17,960
I didn't expect

53
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,960
you to have some skills.

54
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:50,440
Bullying a child

55
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:51,820
is not a real skill.

56
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,560
Sister Gesang,

57
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:57,090
you didn't lie to me.

58
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:58,840
You came to save me.

59
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:02,120
Of course I keep my word.

60
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:05,220
Another one coming to die.

61
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,600
Cut the crap,

62
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:09,520
you wild demon.

63
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,240
Golden Immortal.

64
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,920
I have searched so hard for you.

65
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:12,880
You have cultivated for thousands of years.

66
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:14,760
If you devote yourself to cultivation,

67
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:16,560
your ascension is within reach.

68
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:17,640
Why bother

69
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:19,360
wreaking havoc

70
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,250
and harming the people?

71
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,160
Ascend to immortality?

72
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:29,200
How can the chance to become an immortal be gained easily?

73
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:31,320
You once guarded Sanshan Stream,

74
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:33,250
so you naturally understand this.

75
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:35,520
Why do you deceive me like this?

76
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,840
If so,

77
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:39,039
you should know.

78
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:41,220
Anyone ascending to immortality

79
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:43,200
must first pass the Three Mountain Streams.

80
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,800
They must sever desires to return to the void,

81
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:46,400
and cut off attachments to merge with the Dao,

82
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:48,860
before they can embark on the immortal path.

83
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:55,690
What a 'sever desires to return to the void and cut off attachments to merge with the Dao'.

84
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:58,560
Are immortals truly free from all desires?

85
00:08:59,880 --> 00:09:00,960
If that's true,

86
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:05,100
why did the Golden Immortal feel compassion for my sister?

87
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:08,960
Your sister,

88
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:12,680
Bai Jingqing.

89
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:18,440
What a hypocritical supreme immortal.

90
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:20,640
That's right.

91
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:24,120
Jingqing is my sister.

92
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:29,690
She cultivated hard for a thousand years.

93
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:32,720
Even though she had proven Hunyuan at that time,

94
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:35,920
it was no match for the lingering attachment you left her.

95
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,880
She just had feelings for you,

96
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:39,820
and it made me end up like this.

97
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:43,800
Since you left that thread of love when you met her,

98
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:46,560
she became obsessed with it.

99
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:50,090
Because of you, she severed all emotions and left me.

100
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:52,040
You forcefully turned my carefree long road

101
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:53,840
into a disaster of human suffering.

102
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:55,500
The Way of Heaven has its duty.

103
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,660
Reincarnation has its order.

104
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,040
In this world,

105
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:02,720
good things are hard to perfect.

106
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:10,680
Why bother with the rules of Heaven?

107
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,820
With the Immortal Lord by my side,

108
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:16,360
why sit withered on a cold cliff

109
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:19,280
guarding those pedantic old rules?

110
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:21,660
This immortal path

111
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:24,280
requires ascetic cultivation.

112
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:28,240
Only by perceiving and understanding within

113
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:30,170
can anger and ignorance dissipate

114
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,700
and the mind become clear.

115
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:34,660
If you delusionally think of taking side paths,

116
00:10:34,800 --> 00:10:38,130
it will eventually be like fishing for the moon in the water.

117
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:43,960
If one can prove the Dao and become an immortal,

118
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:46,770
who cares whether the path is orthodox or not?

119
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:53,160
Golden Immortal, you are truly heartless.

120
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:57,330
If you share your divine power with me,

121
00:10:57,760 --> 00:10:59,960
I will let your friends go immediately.

122
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:02,540
I won't hold you back afterwards.

123
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,730
You are an immortal.

124
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:10,800
This is effortless for you.

125
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:13,340
If you insist on refusing,

126
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:18,040
I will refine them all into Nine-Turn Soul-Restoring Pills.

127
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,520
If you refuse to be a vessel,

128
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:26,080
then perish along with them.

129
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,640
How do you know

130
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:35,050
you can definitely beat me?

131
00:11:35,640 --> 00:11:37,840
Your immortal roots have been severed.

132
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:39,280
The way you are now,

133
00:11:40,560 --> 00:11:42,000
how could I not beat you?

134
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:39,800
Ping Jie Qiang Hai Hui.
